729034f-a.title: Richmond: Jewett Avenue - Catherine Court
729034f-a.text:
(1)
Jewett Avenue, at the S.W. corner of Catherine Court, showing the St. John's Evangelical lutheran Church. The view is northward.
March 6, 1930.
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same at a later date.
May 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr
(3)
A view from the east side of Jewett Avenue.
May 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr
